Ready to join?

Give our team a call to discuss your health and wellness goals and we'll create a customized plan to help you achieve them.

Can I change my schedule?

Absolutely! As long as you provide us with at least 45 days' notice, you can switch up your workout days/times up to two times at no extra cost.

What is the cancellation policy?

If you need to reschedule within 45 days, there may be a full payment required for perishable items. However, we're always here to find the best solution for you!

What are the billing terms?

To secure your membership, we ask for a 50% payment upfront with the remaining 50% due 24 hours before your first gym session.

How do I invite guests?

Our user-friendly online platform has an easy-to-navigate "Invitations" feature where you can effortlessly manage and send out gym invites to your friends or let us handle it for you.

Do you offer personal training sessions?

Yes, we do. Simply reach out to our fitness experts and provide your preferences.

Want to know more about our gym facilities?

Can't find the information you're seeking? Let's have a detailed conversation.
